<p><br><font size="+2"><b>
<a name="cq_guru_special"> </a>
<a href="orange-cult_a6.html#ca_guru_special">61</a>.
The Guru Is Extra-Special.</b></font><br>
<p>
The guru is the Messiah, or is God. The guru is the only one in the
world who knows the new Truth. The guru deserves the best of everything.
The guru deserves all of the money, all of the women, and all of the drugs,
because he is extra-special.
<p>
