<p>
And the Rajneeshees raved that Bhagwan Shree
Rajneesh was actually God Himself returning to Earth in Poona, India &#8212;
&quot;Bhagwan&quot; is actually a title that means &quot;embodiment
of God&quot; &#8212;
and they bowed and swooned in ecstasy when he did his daily
