Rajneesh's teachings included, &quot;sex is fun, materialism is good
and Jesus was a madman,&quot; and the claim that he was &quot;the
world's greatest lover.&quot;
Materialism was so good that he had to spend millions of dollars just
to build a huge garage to house all of his Rolls Royces.
(By 1985, he had 93 of them.)<br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;
From his commune in rural eastern Oregon, his people
launched the only germ warfare attack on the USA since the Revolutionary
War (when the British deliberately infected Gen. George Washington's
troops with smallpox). The Rajneeshees infected the salad bars of
several restaurants in The Dalles, Oregon, with salmonella just before
election day, in an attempt to make everyone but their own people
too sick to vote, so that the Rajneeshees could take over the county
